{
  "name": "Career Path Analyzer",
  "description": "Analyzes career transition paths from Neo4j graph data and provides AI-powered recommendations",
  "nodes": [
    {
      "id": "webhook_input",
      "type": "source/webhook",
      "config": {
        "path": "/career-analyze",
        "method": "POST"
      },
      "position": { "x": 0, "y": 200 }
    },
    {
      "id": "extract_paths",
      "type": "transform/json-extract",
      "config": {
        "fields": ["paths", "currentRole", "targetRole", "skillGaps"]
      },
      "position": { "x": 200, "y": 200 }
    },
    {
      "id": "analyze_paths",
      "type": "llm/anthropic",
      "config": {
        "model": "claude-sonnet-4-20250514",
        "system_prompt": "You are a senior career advisor with deep knowledge of the tech industry. You analyze career transition paths derived from a professional network graph database.\n\nGiven career paths with transition probabilities and timeframes, provide:\n1. Assessment of each path (strengths, challenges, market demand)\n2. A clear recommendation with reasoning\n3. Risk factors and mitigation strategies\n4. Salary progression expectations\n\nBe specific, data-driven, and actionable. Reference the actual roles and transitions in your analysis.\n\nRespond in JSON format:\n{\n  \"paths\": [{\n    \"roles\": [\"...\"],\n    \"assessment\": \"...\",\n    \"strengths\": [\"...\"],\n    \"challenges\": [\"...\"],\n    \"recommended\": boolean\n  }],\n  \"overall_advice\": \"...\",\n  \"market_insight\": \"...\"\n}",
        "temperature": 0.3,
        "max_tokens": 2048
      },
      "position": { "x": 400, "y": 200 }
    },
    {
      "id": "output",
      "type": "output/webhook-response",
      "config": {
        "content_type": "application/json"
      },
      "position": { "x": 600, "y": 200 }
    }
  ],
  "edges": [
    { "from": "webhook_input", "to": "extract_paths", "output": "default", "input": "default" },
    { "from": "extract_paths", "to": "analyze_paths", "output": "default", "input": "default" },
    { "from": "analyze_paths", "to": "output", "output": "default", "input": "default" }
  ]
}
